    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "I'm a PM at a 200-person B2B startup, we use Jira today plus a mess of Notion pages."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"I'm a PM at a 200-person B2B startup, we use Jira today plus…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about willingness to pay at $99/mo?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "Honestly $99 is stretching it, we cap tool budgets at $60/seat per month."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"Honestly $99 is stretching it, we cap tool budgets at $60/se…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about competitor comparison (Jira, Asana, Linear)?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "Jira feels heavy but it's what our engineers know. Linear has been eating our developer mindshare."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"Jira feels heavy but it's what our engineers know. Linear ha…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about budget owner and approval process?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "Our CTO approves anything over $50/seat. Under that I can expense it."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"Our CTO approves anything over $50/seat. Under that I can ex…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about features worth paying more for?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "If it saved me 3 hours of standup prep per week I'd pay double."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
